{
  "stem": "13251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He lived there, and he was trained, preparing to live on a kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the first time my brother was happy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he loved it over there-- the community over there, such a friendly environment, out with the other kids.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, him being-- like, he wasn't a well child-- he got better being in that environment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He became stronger and healthier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And somewhere along the line, we joined-- we signed up for Youth Aliyah, which is immigration to Israel-- youth immigration to Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's how I got to Israel because that's one of things we always wanted to do is go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably-- let's see we were in England in '46.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in England three years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It probably took a year or two, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was always-- my dream was always to go to study art, you know, go to get into an art school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in England it's very difficult to get in because they have so many people waiting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I finally got in on a trial basis at a school in London called Camberwell School of Arts and Crafts, and yeah, that was the best school ever went to.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I loved-- that was-- I mean, I can't tell you how much I loved going to that school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, I never waited for the bell to ring to go home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was probably always the last one there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Something I always wanted to do, and I finally made it to that school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After trying, and interviews, and interviews, I finally was accepted.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
